snippet.title: The Awakener: Risen - 2022 TGS Trailer | PS5 & PS4 Games
snippet.description:
The Awakener: Risen is coming to PlayStation in 2023. The war between demons and mortals lasts for thousands of years, now it's time to end it. Build your warrior and fight against demons, even slay the dragons in this medieval world.

#ps5games #ps4games
